	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I loaded all the sprite data on cycle 256 of the previous scanline.  That's probably "good enough" for every existing commercial game (I don't know of any which do mid-frame sprite tricks -- and if they do, they likely shut the PPU off for a few scanlines anyway)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


